quran[7{c,v,t}:
11,13,"kya yeh kehte hain ke paighambar ne yeh kitaab khud ghurr li hai? kaho,"" acha yeh baat hai to is jaisi gharri hui das sortain tum bana lao aur Allah ke siwa aur jo jo ( tumahray mabood ) hain unn ko madad ke liye bulaa satke ho to bulaa lau agar tum ( inhen mabood samajhney mein ) sachey ho"
11,14,"ab agar woh ( tumahray mabood ) tumhari madad ko nahi pahunchte to jaan lau ke yeh Allah ke ilm se nazil hui hai aur yeh ke Allah ke siwa koi haqeeqi mabood nahi hai phir kya tum ( is amar haq ke agay ) sir tasleem khham kar te ho? """
11,15,jo log bas isi duniya ki zindagi aur is ki khooshnumayoon ke taalib hotay hain un ki car guzari ka sara phal hum yahin un ko day dete hain aur is mein un ke sath koi kami nahi ki jati
11,16,magar akhirat mein aisay logon ke liye aag ke siwa kuch nahi hai ( wahan maloom ho jaye ga ke ) jo kuch unhon ne duniya mein banaya woh sab malyamait ho gaya aur ab un ka sara kya dhara mehez baatil hai
11,17,"phir bhala woh shakhs jo apne rab ki taraf se aik saaf shahadat rakhta tha, is ke baad aik gawah bhi parvar-digaar ki taraf se ( is shahadat ki taied mein ) aa gaya, aur pehlay moose ki kitaab rehnuma aur rehmat ke tor par aayi hui bhi mojood thi ( kya woh bhi duniya paraston ki terhan is se inkaar karsaktha hai? ) aisay log to is par imaan hi layein ge aur insani garohoon mein se jo koi is ka inkaar kere to is ke liye jis jagah ka wada hai woh dozakh hai pas ae Peghambar tum iss cheez ki taraf se kisi shak mein nah parna, yeh haq hai tumahray rab ki taraf se magar aksar log nahi mantay"
11,18,aur uss shakhs se barh kar zalim aur kon hoga jo Allah par jhoot gharrey? aisay log apne rab ke huzoor paish hon ge aur gawah shahadat den ge ke yeh hain woh log jinhon ne apne rab par jhoot ghara tha suno! khuda ki laanat hai zaalmon par
11,19,"unn zaalmon par jo khuda ke rastay se logon ko roktay hain, is ke rastay ko ٹیٹرھا karna chahtay hain aur akhirat ka inkaar karte hain"
